IdrPlateCarree
public class IdrEquidistantCylindrical
extends org.geotools.referencing.operation.projection.MapProjection

Equidistant cylindrical projection (EPSG code 9823). In the particular case where the standard_parallel_1 is 0, this projection is also called Plate Carree or Equirectangular. This is used in, for example, WGS84 / Plate Carree (EPSG:32662). References:

  • John P. Snyder (Map Projections - A Working Manual,
    U.S. Geological Survey Professional Paper 1395, 1987)
  • "Coordinate Conversions and Transformations including Formulas",
    EPSG Guidence Note Number 7 part 2, Version 24.
